<h2 id="week-5-overview">Week 5 Overview</h2>
<h3 id="objectives">Objectives</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Introduce and practice the concept of coordinates</li>
  <li>Understand how we can change x and y coordinates to make a Sprite (character) move</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="materials-and-resources">Materials and Resources</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Materials needed: <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=170rc8PcbMsOjUpwzcACI3NwAf2seUrZuRN2DMWgh-Ks">Treasure Hunt worksheet</a></li>
