  <li>Week 5 Worksheet Solution: <a href="https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/379936362/">Part 1</a>, <a href="https://scratch.mit.edu/projects/379938822/">Part 2</a></li>
  <li>Week 5 <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=1ET4Xll4KaG6YiNtz6cbxUDlPvIzTVhyPYRxgvkfljvw">Presentation</a></li>
