<h3 id="lesson-plan-overview">Lesson Plan Overview</h3>
<p>View our detailed lesson plan <a href="https://drive.google.com/open?id=11OWAQwI0b0nw6I13je9Ji5EUYoS6kw6xUHnMzigRA8c">here</a>.</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Introduction</strong> (5 min): Review variables</li>
  <li><strong>Unplugged Activity</strong> (10 min): Review coordinates and do Treasure Hunt activity</li>
  <li><strong>Live Coding</strong> (5 min): Show how to use coordinates in Scratch</li>
  <li><strong>Worksheet</strong> (30 min): Log into Scratch accounts and work on the worksheet</li>
  <li><strong>Wrap up</strong> (5 min): See how coordinates fit with the maze activity</li>
</ul>

