<h3 id="part-3-apple-chasing">Part 3: Apple Chasing!</h3>

<p>Donâ€™t get rid of your last project yet - itâ€™s time to make a game! Whenever Scratch runs into the apple, he should get a point, and the apple should run away from him!</p>

<p><img src="/assets/images/week5/img3.png" alt="image #3" /></p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>- Add a new sprite with the + Sprite button!

- We need a new variable 'score.' When we click the flag, the score should be set to 0. 

- Then, we should have a loop that runs forever, checking each time if Scratch is touching the apple.

- When he is, he should get a point and the apple should move!
</code></pre></div></div>

